room_title: Escape room "The Game Room" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
room_description: Explore the rooms and discover secrets to open the hidden escape door. In order to find your way to freedom, you must outwit Morto the puppet by solving his riddles. Here you’ll find such rare artifacts as a Werewolf Anatomical Research Case, a 1800’s Vampire Hunting Kit, the remains from a Fiji Mermaid, just to name a few.
